{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"56512-my-best-friend","title":"Ang Matalik kong Kaibigan","description":"Nais mo bang magkaroon ng espesyal na kaibigan? Silipin ang aklat na ito at baka makilala mo na ang iyong napaka-espesyal na kaibigan!","language":"Filipino","langCode":"fil","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Kaye Sucgang"],"illustrators":["Suvidha Mistry"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/56512-my-best-friend"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/704882/size3/b1586d957cd76fc5ad2d07442f85401c.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/704882/size6/b1586d957cd76fc5ad2d07442f85401c.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/12939/size6/26f3c562e8fcf285da64ace4885497a2.jpg","text":"Mayroon akong kaibigan. Nakatira siya sa aming bahay.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/12940/size6/d07a196027366d86d218485a16115cef.jpg","text":"Tuwing masaya ako, masaya rin siya.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/12941/size6/9968ed9b842685f573b114b9a2be8e6a.jpg","text":"Tuwing umiiyak ako, umiiyak din siya.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/12942/size6/7f19ca3a7f4392ae1737ad6f7ba722e6.jpg","text":"Pero hindi ko naririnig ang kaniyang boses. Nakatira sa loob ng salamin ang kaibigan ko.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/12943/size6/f77bed787eca6e623588fd4492456666.jpg","text":"\"Lumabas ka na,\"sabi ko sa kaniya, \"maglalaro tayo.\"Ngunit hindi siya lumabas.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/12944/size6/0ab978d66dc04fbd958537accfaf3474.jpg","text":"Hindi ako masaya kaya natulog na lang ako.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/12945/size6/f2d91399e3710afc2ab72f1a4251ae1f.jpg","text":"Lumabas siya sa salamin sa aking panaginip! At labis kaming nagsaya.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/12946/size6/99927082c4c7183837255183b81f106f.jpg","text":"Sabay kaming naglaro, tumakbo, sumigaw at tumili.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/12947/size6/193694c2078e2b794802233069bfca43.jpg","text":"Kinakausap niya ako sa tuwing kinakausap ko siya.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/12948/size6/2fdc1d0c194d45e607462e4a77a7b9b4.jpg","text":"Sa umaga, bumabalik ang aking kaibigan sa salamin.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/12949/size6/e6d48b6c13538e56e67d69f9f907c03e.jpg","text":"Pero okay lang iyon sa akin. Maglalaro naman kaming muli sa aking mga panaginip!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":102}}